responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "12E821474455D841550DD28FF50425B5", "I\'ve seen Sighted scavengers skulking from the gates of Old Carphin into these surrounding woods - and I have myself caught goblins creeping through the brush to meet with them. Shamans and animal tamers alike sully these groves, and it is my belief that the Sighted are wooing these pests with magic to strengthen their animal servants. This cannot stand.")
